source.name: Monthly Wholesale Trade
source.description: Tracks month-to-month trends for sales and inventories of U.S. distributors, jobbers, drop shippers, and import/export merchants, excluding manufacturers' sales branches or offices (MSBOs).  Provides constant dollar values of sales and end-of-month inventories.
